* If the transfered bytes of a profiles entry (statistics) were larger than
  32bit they were shown (and saved) as 0. Fixed.
  [Martyn Capewell/Torsten "ToDi" Ketelsen]

* "Add"-button in ADT-mode was not ghosted if not connected. Fixed.
